Drawing.addDoodle
	Doodle Subclass constructor
		Doodle Class constructor
			Doodle subclass setParameterDefaults (new doodles only)
			Doodle subclass setPropertyDefaults


	Doodle subclass setParameter (from parameter defaults array)
		Doodle class setParameter
		

Parameters can be set in the following ways;

	Mouse dragging (only affects simple parameters)
		calls validateParameter for range only
		set parameter calls update dependencies
		
	HTML events can affect all parameters
	
	
Validation method ensures that value is in correct format and always outputs a string
It takes a parameter of any type, and returns the validated value

set parameter takes a validated string value, and sets type appropriately

SetParameterWithAnimation

	Get list of simple parameters involved
	Work out their target values
	Start an animation for each one
			
			
			Next task: Add a value to dependentParameterValues = function(_parameter) to calculate future values


	
